# CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Permissive

This is a permissive licence which allows you to use the hardware description
files (Verilog RTL, constraints, synthesis scripts) in any way you wish,
including for commercial purposes, as long as you preserve the copyright notice.

Full terms: https://ohwr.org/project/cernohl/wikis/Documents/CERN-OHL-version-2

In summary:
- You may redistribute the hardware descriptions in any form
- You may modify them and distribute modified versions
- You may use them in commercial products
- You must preserve the copyright notice and this licence text
- No warranty or liability is provided

This licence covers all files in this directory and its subdirectories
unless another licence is explicitly stated.
